{"id":"lyon-1h1.12","title":"Step 1: Build transcribe feature","description":"Build the transcribe step: video URL -> timestamped transcript in DB.\n\nAPI:\n- POST /api/transcribe { videoUrl: string }\n- GET /api/pipeline-runs (paginated)\n- GET /api/pipeline-runs/:id (single run)\n- GET /api/pipeline-runs/:id/clips (clips for run)\n\nDB: queued->transcribing->transcribed|failed\nDownload from R2, run Whisper, store transcript. Cleanup temp files.\n6 error codes: TRANSCRIBE_*\n\nCREATE: features/(business)/transcribe/ (CLAUDE.md, routes.ts, service.ts, service.test.ts)\nMODIFY: platform/server/routes.ts\n\nACCEPTANCE:\n- Full transcribe flow works\n- All 4 GET+POST endpoints work\n- 6 error paths tested\n- Temp cleanup on success AND failure\n- 100% coverage (8 tests)","status":"open","priority":0,"issue_type":"task","estimated_minutes":120,"created_at":"2026-04-07T21:00:45.711916Z","created_by":"claude-agent","updated_at":"2026-04-07T21:46:07.190251Z","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0,"labels":["feature","step1"],"dependencies":[{"issue_id":"lyon-1h1.12","depends_on_id":"lyon-1h1","type":"parent-child","created_at":"2026-04-07T21:00:45.711916Z","created_by":"claude-agent","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"lyon-1h1.12","depends_on_id":"lyon-1h1.11","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-04-07T21:00:45.711916Z","created_by":"claude-agent","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"lyon-1h1.12","depends_on_id":"lyon-1h1.3","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-04-07T21:00:45.711916Z","created_by":"claude-agent","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"lyon-1h1.12","depends_on_id":"lyon-1h1.4","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-04-07T21:00:45.711916Z","created_by":"claude-agent","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"lyon-1h1.12","depends_on_id":"lyon-1h1.5","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-04-07T21:00:45.711916Z","created_by":"claude-agent","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"lyon-1h1.12","depends_on_id":"lyon-1h1.7","