{"id":"lyon-1h1.13","title":"Step 2: Build clip-select feature","description":"POST /api/clip-select {pipelineRunId}\nDB: transcribed->selecting->selected|failed. Creates clips rows.\nClaude reads transcript, picks 15 segments. Re-selection DELETEs old clips first.\nValidate timestamps against durationSeconds.\n6 error codes: CLIP_SELECT_*\n\nCREATE: features/(business)/clip-select/ (CLAUDE.md, routes.ts, service.ts, service.test.ts)\n\nACCEPTANCE: Claude identifies segments, re-selection safe, timestamps validated, 100% coverage (7 tests)","status":"open","priority":0,"issue_type":"task","estimated_minutes":120,"created_at":"2026-04-07T21:00:45.974907Z","created_by":"claude-agent","updated_at":"2026-04-07T21:00:45.974907Z","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0,"labels":["feature","step2"],"dependencies":[{"issue_id":"lyon-1h1.13","depends_on_id":"lyon-1h1","type":"parent-child","created_at":"2026-04-07T21:00:45.974907Z","created_by":"claude-agent","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"lyon-1h1.13","depends_on_id":"lyon-1h1.12","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-04-07T21:00:45.974907Z","created_by":"claude-agent","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""}]}
{"id":"lyon-1h1.14","title":"Step 3: Build clip-cut feature","description":"Build clip cutting: definitions -> video files in R2 via ffmpeg.\n\nAPI:\n- POST /api/clip-cut { pipelineRunId } (all approved clips)\n- POST /api/clip-cut { clipId } (single clip retry)\n- GET /api/clips/:id (single clip with posts)\n- GET /api/clips/:id/posts (posts for a clip)\n\nDB: selected->cutting->cut|failed. Per-clip cutStatus tracking.\nffmpeg cuts, upload to R2. Partial failure returns 207.\n6 error codes: CLIP_CUT_*\n\nCREATE: features/(business)/clip-cut/ (CLAUDE.md, routes.ts, service.ts, service.test.ts)\n\nACCEPTANCE:\n- ffmpeg cuts clips correctly\n- R2 upload with valid URLs\n- All 4 GET+POST endpoints work\n- Partial failure: failed clips marked individually\n- Temp cleanup on success AND failure\n- 100% coverage (7 tests)","status":"open","priority":0,"issue_type":"task","estimated_minutes":120,"created_at":"2026-04-07T21:00:46.235931Z","created_by":"claude-agent","updated_at":"2026-04-07T21:46:15.729549Z","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0,"labels":["feature","step3"],"dependencies":[{"issue_id":"lyon-1h1.14","depends_on_id":"lyon-1h1","type":"parent-child","created_at":"2026-04-07T21:00:46.235931Z","created_by":"claude-agent","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"lyon-1h1.14","depends_on_id":"lyon-1h1.13","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-04-07T21:00:46.235931Z","created_by":"claude-agent","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"lyon-1h1.14","depends_on_id":"lyon-1h1.6","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-04-07T21:00:46.235931Z","created_by":"claude-agent","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""}]}
