{"id":"lyon-1h1","title":"Epic: BD Podcast Distribution Pipeline (Phase 1)","description":"Business Decisions Phase 1: automated podcast-to-social-media pipeline.\nSKILL-DRIVEN ARCHITECTURE: NO AI API keys. All AI thinking runs in user's Claude Code subscription via skills. Server endpoints are RECEIVERS (validate + save), never CALLERS of AI.\n7 steps: Transcribe (Whisper) -> Select Clips (SKILL) -> Cut Clips (ffmpeg) -> Generate Metadata (SKILL) -> Distribute (Upload-Post) -> Collect Analytics -> Generate Insights (SKILL).\nSteps 2, 4, 7 are skill-driven: Claude Code reads data, thinks, POSTs results to server endpoints.\nArchitecture: Step-based workflows, PostgreSQL source of truth, R2 object storage, Upload-Post for posting.\nEach step = independent feature folder + API endpoint + DB state transition.\n13 accounts across TikTok, Instagram, Facebook, X, YouTube.\nTarget: <2 hours from recording to all posts distributed.","status":"open","priority":0,"issue_type":"epic","created_at":"2026-04-07T21:00:42.668717Z","created_by":"claude-agent","updated_at":"2026-04-07T23:35:18.564304Z","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0}
