{"id":"lyon-1h1.22","title":"Update providers/CLAUDE.md with ProviderError pattern","description":"Update the existing providers/CLAUDE.md to document the ProviderError pattern used by all new BD providers.\n\nAdd to Critical Rules:\n- All provider functions throw ProviderError on failure (not raw HTTP/SDK errors)\n- ProviderError shape: { provider: string, operation: string, statusCode: number, rawResponse: unknown }\n- Feature layer catches ProviderError and maps to throwError() codes\n- Never let raw AWS/Upload-Post/Whisper errors leak to the feature layer\n\nAdd to Recipe section:\n```typescript\nclass ProviderError extends Error {\n  constructor(\n    public provider: string,\n    public operation: string,\n    public statusCode: number,\n    public rawResponse: unknown,\n  ) { super(`${provider}.${operation} failed (${statusCode})`) }\n}\n```\n\nMODIFY: providers/CLAUDE.md\n\nACCEPTANCE:\n- ProviderError pattern documented\n- All 4 new providers reference it\n- Existing providers (email, payments, content) unaffected","status":"closed","priority":1,"issue_type":"chore","assignee":"henriquemeireles","created_at":"2026-04-07T21:46:27.771504Z","created_by":"henriquemeireles","updated_at":"2026-04-07T21:55:38.978484Z","closed_at":"2026-04-07T21:55:38.977737Z","close_reason":"Created providers/errors.ts with ProviderError class. Updated providers/CLAUDE.md with error wrapping rules and pattern. 62 tests pass.","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0,"labels":["chore","provider"],"dependencies":[{"issue_id":"lyon-1h1.22","depends_on_id":"lyon-1h1","type":"parent-child","created_at":"2026-04-07T21:46:27.771504Z","created_by":"henriquemeireles","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"lyon-1h1.22","depends_on_id":"lyon-1h1.5","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-04-07T21:46:27.771504Z","created_by":"henriquemeireles","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""}]}
