{"id":"lyon-1h1.23","title":"Create /select-clips skill (AI step for clip selection)","description":"Claude Code skill that does the AI thinking for Step 2.\n\nCREATE: .claude/skills/select-clips/SKILL.md\n\nThe skill:\n1. GET /api/pipeline-runs/:id — read transcript\n2. Claude Code analyzes transcript, picks 15 best 30-60 second segments\n3. For each: score 1-10, suggest title, note platform fit, extract snippet\n4. POST /api/clip-select {pipelineRunId, clips: [...]} — server validates + saves\n\nThis is the AI LAYER. The server endpoint (lyon-1h1.13) is the receiver.\nSkill runs in user's Claude Code subscription. Zero API cost.\n\nACCEPTANCE: Skill reads transcript, produces valid clip definitions, POSTs to endpoint successfully","status":"open","priority":0,"issue_type":"task","estimated_minutes":30,"created_at":"2026-04-07T23:36:24.190086Z","created_by":"henriquemeireles","updated_at":"2026-04-07T23:36:24.190086Z","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0,"dependencies":[{"issue_id":"lyon-1h1.23","depends_on_id":"lyon-1h1","type":"parent-child","created_at":"2026-04-07T23:36:24.190086Z","created_by":"henriquemeireles","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"lyon-1h1.23","depends_on_id":"lyon-1h1.13","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-04-07T23:36:24.190086Z","created_by":"henriquemeireles","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""}]}
{"id":"lyon-1h1.24","title":"Create /generate-metadata skill (AI step for metadata)","description":"Claude Code skill that does the AI thinking for Step 4.\n\nCREATE: .claude/skills/generate-metadata/SKILL.md\n\nThe skill:\n1. GET /api/pipeline-runs/:id/clips — read cut clips with transcriptSnippets\n2. GET /api/platform-accounts — read platform char limits\n3. Claude Code generates per-platform descriptions, hashtags, CTAs\n4. POST /api/metadata-generate {pipelineRunId, metadata: [...]} — server validates + saves\n\nThis is the AI LAYER. The server endpoint (lyon-1h1.15) is the receiver.\nSkill runs in user's Claude Code subscription. Zero API cost.\n\nACCEPTANCE: Skill reads clips + platform rules, produces valid metadata per clip+platform, POSTs to endpoint","status":"open","priority":0,"issue_type":"task","estimated_minutes":30,"created_at":"2026-04-07T23:36:32.578284Z","created_by":"henriquemeireles","updated_at":"2026-04-07T23:36:32.578284Z","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0,"dependencies":[{"issue_id":"lyon-1h1.24","depends_on_id":"lyon-1h1","type":"parent-child","created_at":"2026-04-07T23:36:32.578284Z","created_by":"henriquemeireles","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"lyon-1h1.24","depends_on_id":"lyon-1h1.15","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-04-07T23:36:32.578284Z","created_by":"henriquemeireles","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""}]}
{"id":"lyon-1h1.25","title":"Create /whats-working skill (AI step for insights)","description":"Claude Code skill that does the AI thinking for Step 7.\n\nCREATE: .claude/skills/whats-working/SKILL.md\n\nThe skill:\n1. GET /api/analytics — read engagement metrics across posts\n2. Claude Code analyzes patterns: what content, platforms, times perform best\n3. Generate ONE actionable recommendation with supporting data\n4. POST /api/insight-generate {dateRange, recommendation, supportingData} — server validates + saves\n\nThis is the AI LAYER. The server endpoint (lyon-1h1.18) is the receiver.\nSkill runs in user's Claude Code subscription. Zero API cost.\n\nACCEPTANCE: Skill reads analytics, produces actionable insight, POSTs to endpoint","status":"open","priority":0,"issue_type":"task","estimated_minutes":30,"created_at":"2026-04-07T23:36:40.015737Z","created_by":"henriquemeireles","updated_at":"2026-04-07T23:36:40.015737Z","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0,"dependencies":[{"issue_id":"lyon-1h1.25","depends_on_id":"lyon-1h1","type":"parent-child","created_at":"2026-04-07T23:36:40.015737Z","created_by":"henriquemeireles","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"lyon-1h1.25","depends_on_id":"lyon-1h1.18","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-04-07T23:36:40.015737Z","created_by":"henriquemeireles","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""}]}
{"id":"lyon-1h1.26","title":"Create /process-episode master skill (orchestrates full pipeline)","description":"Master Claude Code skill that orchestrates the full podcast pipeline.\n\nCREATE: .claude/skills/process-episode/SKILL.md\n\nThe skill chains all steps:\n1. POST /api/transcribe {videoUrl} — wait for transcript\n2. GET /api/pipeline-runs/:id — read transcript\n3. [AI THINKS] Pick clips → POST /api/clip-select (uses /select-clips logic inline)\n4. POST /api/clip-cut {pipelineRunId} — wait for cuts\n5. GET /api/pipeline-runs/:id/clips — read cut clips\n6. [AI THINKS] Generate metadata → POST /api/metadata-generate (uses /generate-metadata logic inline)\n7. POST /api/post-distribute {pipelineRunId} — distribute to platforms\n\nPhase 1 (auto mode): runs straight through, no pauses.\nPhase 3 (platform mode): pauses at approval gates.\n\nACCEPTANCE: Full pipeline from video URL to posted clips in one skill invocation","status":"open","priority":0,"issue_type":"task","estimated_minutes":45,"created_at":"2026-04-07T23:36:51.603389Z","created_by":"henriquemeireles","updated_at":"2026-04-07T23:36:51.603389Z","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0,"dependencies":[{"issue_id":"lyon-1h1.26","depends_on_id":"lyon-1h1","type":"parent-child","created_at":"2026-04-07T23:36:51.603389Z","created_by":"henriquemeireles","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"lyon-1h1.26","depends_on_id":"lyon-1h1.19","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-04-07T23:36:51.603389Z","created_by":"henriquemeireles","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"lyon-1h1.26","depends_on_id":"lyon-1h1.23","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-04-07T23:36:51.603389Z","created_by":"henriquemeireles","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"lyon-1h1.26","depends_on_id":"lyon-1h1.24","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-04-07T23:36:51.603389Z","created_by":"henriquemeireles","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""}]}
