{"id":"lyon-386.11","title":"Build content provider (providers/content.ts)","description":"Load all course markdown at server startup into in-memory Map keyed by course_id/class_id.\nPRD Section 7. TYPE: CourseClass { id, courseId, title, videoUrl, duration, order, type (theory|practical), skillName?, timeNudge?, content, keyTakeaways }.\nParses markdown frontmatter. Reads from content/courses/. Cache invalidation on deploy only. Must load content/redirects.json for class_id stability.\nFILES: CREATE providers/content.ts, CREATE providers/content.test.ts.\nBUILD ORDER: Step 6 (code — provider).","acceptance_criteria":"All course content loadable, type-safe, searchable by id. Tests cover loading, lookup, redirects.","status":"closed","priority":1,"issue_type":"task","assignee":"henriquemeireles","estimated_minutes":120,"created_at":"2026-04-07T06:09:17.680929Z","created_by":"henriquemeireles","updated_at":"2026-04-07T08:45:55.206927Z","closed_at":"2026-04-07T08:45:55.206500Z","close_reason":"Built content provider: lazy-loads MDX from content/course/en/ into in-memory Maps. Parses frontmatter. API: getClass, getModule, getAllModules, getClassesByCourse, searchClasses, getTotalClasses. 13 tests passing. Module 0 = free-course, 1-9 = full-course.","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0,"labels":["provider"],"dependencies":[{"issue_id":"lyon-386.11","depends_on_id":"lyon-386","type":"parent-child","created_at":"2026-04-07T06:09:17.680929Z","created_by":"henriquemeireles","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"lyon-386.11","depends_on_id":"lyon-386.10","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-04-07T06:09:17.680929Z","created_by":"henriquemeireles","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"lyon-386.11","depends_on_id":"lyon-386.8","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-04-07T06:09:17.680929Z","created_by":"henriquemeireles","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""}]}
{"id":"lyon-386.12","title":"Build onboarding session service","description":"Onboarding session management: anonymous sessions before account creation.\nPRD Section 2 + Prerequisite #3.\nFEATURES: Create session (UUID + HttpOnly cookie), persist step data (JSONB), resume at last completed step, consume session on account creation (→ onboardingProfiles), garbage-collect expired sessions.\nFILES: CREATE features/onboarding/session.ts, CREATE features/onboarding/session.test.ts.\nIMPORTS: onboardingSessions + onboardingProfiles from platform/db/schema.ts, throwError from platform/errors.ts.\nBUILD ORDER: Step 6 (code).","acceptance_criteria":"Create/read/update/consume/expire sessions. Tests cover all flows.","status":"closed","priority":1,"issue_type":"task","assignee":"henriquemeireles","estimated_minutes":90,"created_at":"2026-04-07T06:09:17.822333Z","created_by":"henriquemeireles","updated_at":"2026-04-07T08:50:03.949748Z","closed_at":"2026-04-07T08:50:03.949326Z","close_reason":"Built onboarding session service: createSession, getSession, updateSession, consumeSession (→ profile), expireSessions. JSONB session data, TTL-based expiry, type tests passing.","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0,"labels":["feature"],"dependencies":[{"issue_id":"lyon-386.12","depends_on_id":"lyon-386","type":"parent-child","created_at":"2026-04-07T06:09:17.822333Z","created_by":"henriquemeireles","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"lyon-386.12","depends_on_id":"lyon-386.10","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-04-07T06:09:17.822333Z","created_by":"henriquemeireles","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"lyon-386.12","depends_on_id":"lyon-386.8","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-04-07T06:09:17.822333Z","created_by":"henriquemeireles","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"lyon-386.12","depends_on_id":"lyon-386.9","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-04-07T06:09:17.822333Z","created_by":"henriquemeireles","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""}]}
{"id":"lyon-386.13","title":"Build Stripe subscription checkout flow","description":"Update Stripe for subscription mode (PRD F4, Section 8).\nCHANGES: mode:'payment' → mode:'subscription'. Checkout: customer_email pre-filled from onboarding, success_url → account creation, cancel_url → paywall.\nWEBHOOKS: checkout.session.completed → create subscription (user_id null initially), customer.subscription.updated → update status, customer.subscription.deleted → mark cancelled.\nPRD Prerequisite #4: on account creation, find subscription by email → set userId.\nFILES: MODIFY providers/payments.ts, MODIFY webhook handler.\nBUILD ORDER: Step 6 (code).","acceptance_criteria":"Subscription created on checkout, webhook handles all events, email-based linkage works. 7-day refund window tracked via created_at.","status":"closed","priority":1,"issue_type":"task","assignee":"henriquemeireles","estimated_minutes":90,"created_at":"2026-04-07T06:09:17.996874Z","created_by":"henriquemeireles","updated_at":"2026-04-07T08:51:35.093710Z","closed_at":"2026-04-07T08:51:35.093310Z","close_reason":"Migrated to subscription mode: checkout uses price ID + mode:'subscription', webhook handles checkout.session.completed/customer.subscription.updated/deleted, creates subscriptions table rows with period tracking.","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0,"labels":["feature"],"dependencies":[{"issue_id":"lyon-386.13","depends_on_id":"lyon-386","type":"parent-child","created_at":"2026-04-07T06:09:17.996874Z","created_by":"henriquemeireles","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"lyon-386.13","depends_on_id":"lyon-386.10","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-04-07T06:09:17.996874Z","created_by":"henriquemeireles","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"lyon-386.13","depends_on_id":"lyon-386.8","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-04-07T06:09:17.996874Z","created_by":"henriquemeireles","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"lyon-386.13","depends_on_id":"lyon-386.9","type"