{"id":"lyon-386.14","title":"Build progress tracking service","description":"Class-level, course_id-scoped progress tracking, no hard sequential gates.\nPRD Section 3 Flow 1, Feature F2.\nFEATURES: Mark class complete (user_id, class_id, course_id, completed_at), get progress for user, get progress per module, calculate overall %, determine current class. No hard gates. Soft time nudge text from module metadata.\nFILES: CREATE features/course/progress.ts, CREATE features/course/progress.test.ts.\nBUILD ORDER: Step 6 (code).","acceptance_criteria":"CRUD on progress, % calculations correct, no hard gates, API < 200ms.","status":"closed","priority":1,"issue_type":"task","assignee":"henriquemeireles","estimated_minutes":90,"created_at":"2026-04-07T06:09:18.303447Z","created_by":"henriquemeireles","updated_at":"2026-04-07T08:57:43.516007Z","closed_at":"2026-04-07T08:57:43.515600Z","close_reason":"Built progress tracking: markClassComplete, getUserProgress, getModuleProgress (% calc), getOverallProgress, getCurrentClass. 4 pure logic tests + 9 access tests = 13 passing.","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0,"labels":["feature"],"dependencies":[{"issue_id":"lyon-386.14","depends_on_id":"lyon-386","type":"parent-child","created_at":"2026-04-07T06:09:18.303447Z","created_by":"henriquemeireles","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"lyon-386.14","depends_on_id":"lyon-386.8","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-04-07T06:09:18.303447Z","created_by":"henriquemeireles","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"lyon-386.14","depends_on_id":"lyon-386.9","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-04-07T06:09:18.303447Z","created_by":"henriquemeireles","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""}]}
