{"id":"lyon-386.37","title":"Build AI skills for Claude Cowork (Phases 1-4)","description":"Build 4 Claude Cowork skills for methodology Phases 1-4 (PRD Section 6, Week 6-7). V1 ships Phases 1-4 minimum (Prepare-to-Execute gap). Skills 5-8 deferred to V1.1.\nSKILLS: (1) /state-map — asks about finances, health, relationships, career. Outputs state-map/raw.md + document.md. (2) /target-state — describes desired life conditions. Reads state-map. (3) /constraint — rates obstacles, gut-checks. Reads state-map + target-state. (4) /decide — names decision, date, witness. Reads constraint.\nRULES: NEVER decide for user. NEVER replace course. NEVER break cross-skill context. Save raw.md (exact words) + document.md (structured). Each skill reads previous skill output.\nFILES: CREATE content/skills/state-map/, target-state/, constraint/, decide/ with skill definition files.\nBUILD ORDER: Step 7 (parallel with weeks 4-5).\nACCEPTANCE: All 4 skills run in Claude Cowork, ask questions, save raw.md + document.md, cross-skill context works.","status":"closed","priority":1,"issue_type":"task","assignee":"henriquemeireles","created_at":"2026-04-07T06:55:07.312406Z","created_by":"henriquemeireles","updated_at":"2026-04-07T09:07:17.853962Z","closed_at":"2026-04-07T09:07:17.853507Z","close_reason":"Built 4 Claude Cowork skills: /state-map (5 domains, facts+ratings+avoidance), /target-state (observable conditions, Tuesday test, ownership check), /constraint (3 candidates, rate, gut-check, choose ONE), /decide (name, date, witness, accountability). Cross-skill context: each reads previous outputs. raw.md + document.md saved for each.","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0,"labels":["feature"],"dependencies":[{"issue_id":"lyon-386.37","depends_on_id":"lyon-386","type":"parent-child","created_at":"2026-04-07T06:55:07.312406Z","created_by":"henriquemeireles","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""}]}
{"id":"lyon-386.38","title":"Build GDPR/privacy endpoints (account deletion + data export)","description":"Account deletion and data export endpoints (PRD Section 8 Privacy). Decision data is deeply personal.\nENDPOINTS: DELETE /api/account — deletes user + all data (profile, progress, wins, cancels Stripe sub). GET /api/account/export — returns JSON with all user data. Cookie consent banner.\nFILES: CREATE features/account/privacy.ts, privacy.test.ts, routes. MODIFY platform/server/routes.ts.\nBUILD ORDER: Step 6.\nACCEPTANCE: DELETE removes all user data (verified via DB query). Export returns complete JSON. Tests cover both.","status":"closed","priority":2,"issue_type":"task","assignee":"henriquemeireles","created_at":"2026-04-07T06:55:07.569293Z","created_by":"henriquemeireles","updated_at":"2026-04-07T09:01:05.424869Z","closed_at":"2026-04-07T09:01:05.424327Z","close_reason":"Built GDPR endpoints: GET /api/account/export (full data export), DELETE /api/account (cascading deletion of all user data). Auth required on both.","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0,"labels":["feature"],"dependencies":[{"issue_id":"lyon-386.38","depends_on_id":"lyon-386","type":"parent-child","created_at":"2026-04-07T06:55:07.569293Z","created_by":"henriquemeireles","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"lyon-386.38","depends_on_id":"lyon-386.8","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-04-07T06:55:07.569293Z","created_by":"henriquemeireles","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""}]}
